In order to print the list you need to use `while` with the same condition in your `displayList()` function.
The while loop running over the list until that `node-&gt;next` will pointed to a `NULL` value (Which means that this is the end of the list).

In the `main()` you only need to initialize one list and add all the values into it.

In addition, a code style recommendation is to start with a capital letter and have a capital letter for each new word It&#39;s useful to distinguish between functions and classes, for example:

